The paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, specifically the study of interval permutation segment graphs. This topic falls under several CS sub-categories, including Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Game Theory and Decision Making (cs.GT), and Data Structures and Randomized Algorithms (cs.DSRT).
